# Bob Generated Output

This folder contains the final output generated by IBM Bob during the demo.

## Purpose

The generated output helps others:
- See the end result of working with Bob
- Compare input vs. output to understand transformations
- Evaluate the quality and accuracy of Bob's work
- Learn what's possible with Bob's capabilities

## What to Include

### Generated Files
- Code files created or modified by Bob
- Documentation generated by Bob
- Configuration files
- Test files
- Any other artifacts produced

### Comparison Files
- Side-by-side comparisons of before/after (if applicable)
- Diff files showing changes made
- Annotations explaining significant changes

### Validation Results
- Test results showing the output works
- Linter or formatter output
- Build logs or compilation results
- Performance metrics (if relevant)

## Organization Tips

- Mirror the structure of input files when possible for easy comparison
- Use clear naming to indicate which files are new vs. modified
- Include timestamps or version numbers if multiple iterations exist
- Add comments in generated code to highlight Bob's contributions

## Example Structure

```
Bob Generated Output/
├── README.md (this file)
├── src/
│   ├── app.js (modified by Bob)
│   └── new-feature.js (created by Bob)
├── tests/
│   └── app.test.js (generated tests)
└── docs/
    └── api-documentation.md (generated docs)
```

## Quality Notes

Document any observations about the output:
- What worked exceptionally well
- Any manual adjustments needed
- Edge cases or limitations discovered
- Suggestions for improvement
